念<br />\n講真我宜家食銀咖哩真係食回憶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBTW果陣叫銀座二丁目"},{"pid":"bd166bc5e81272f523131accb713f882e7e3172b","tid":416810,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:57:34.000Z","msg":"我食果間鐵碟都無  得即棄膠碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返工成日食"},{"pid":"7c2b6b24017a614e4a935799d22511157d454801","tid":416810,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T17:01:14.000Z","msg":"唔知佢啲肉碎定飯定肉<br />\n次次食完都好撚un胃，好撚唔舒服<br />\n但隔一排又好犯賤咁去食"},{"pid":"98fac10f7a967260b169c3a165ecf811148ead8d","tid":416810,"uid":150483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T17:13:23.000Z","msg":"好過八方雲集先，用紙餐具裝住<br />\n大食會咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申，學校附近兩間都有，中學狗都唔屌"},{"pid":"305e12c3e30075ebe8137285517b1e52aa15f1dd","tid":416810,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:27:52.000Z","msg":"想知加飯係咪免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又唔知加到盡有幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a21e28b686ea4abba3952cfc46b130b7d162dc1","tid":416810,"uid":41270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知佢啲肉碎定飯定肉<br />\n次次食完都好撚un胃，好撚唔舒服<br />\n但隔一排又好犯賤咁去食</blockquote><br />\n原來唔係得我會咁<br />\n每次食完都un到有啲想嘔<br />\n我仲以為係自己胃弱"},{"pid":"daf48fcc71f61f61c5dd844f783f90f5e513b2ca","tid":416810,"uid":1902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T10:52:10.000Z","msg":"D 咖哩我覺得幾好食<br />\n但隻碟會一路食一路轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}